"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Generic helper method that makes a request to PubMed.\n\nParameters:\n    - url           Str, last part of the URL that is requested (will\n                    be combined with the base url)\n    - parameters    Dict, parameters to use for the request\n    - output        Str, type of output that is requested (defaults to\n                    JSON but can be used to retrieve XML)\n\nReturns:\n    - response      Dict / str, if the response is valid JSON it will\n                    be parsed before returning, otherwise a string is\n                    returend"]}, {"name": "pymed.api.PubMed._getArticles", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": {"name": "object", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.object", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "article_ids", "type": {"name": "list", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.list", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "list", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.list", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Helper method that batches a list of article IDs and retrieves the content.\n\nParameters:\n    - article_ids   List, article IDs.\n\nReturns:\n    - articles      List, article objects."]}, {"name": "pymed.api.PubMed._getArticleIds", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": {"name": "object", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.object", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "query", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "max_results", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "list", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.list", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Helper method to retrieve the article IDs for a query.\n\nParameters:\n    - query     